{"tid":2358542,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"英國政府：所有入境旅客下周起必須提供72小時武肺病毒測試報告","createTime":"2021-01-08T08:10:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T09:24:40.000Z","uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a3a492519bdc576976a26f6314b6f84d5c438257","tid":2358542,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:10:13.000Z","msg":"英國政府最新公布，所有入境旅客下周起必須提供72小時COVID 19的病毒測試報告。<br />\n<br />\n旅客在出境前要出示對病毒呈陰性反應的報告，並於入境時由關員查核。違者可被罰款&pound;500。根據現時「旅客通道」政策下，入境後要隔離的人士仍須自我隔離10天，即使有陰性報告。（香港屬於豁免隔離地區）<br />\n<br />\n旅客入境仍須填報入境健康申報表格及受限於所有封城措施。<br />\n<br />\nMandatory COVID-19 testing introduced to bolster border measures<br />\n<br />\nInternational arrivals required to prove negative COVID-19 test result before departure for England.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.gov.uk/government/news/mandatory-covid-19-testing-introduced-to-bolster-border-measures\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.uk%2Fgovernment%2Fnews%2Fmandatory-covid-19-testing-introduced-to-bolster-border-measures&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTITC6QH3F2wvzJ1VFJz7MVw4%3D&h=27222547\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.gov.uk/government/news/mandatory-covid-19-testing-introduced-to-bolster-border-measures</a>"},{"pid":"f5abe3f81e348dc9812d398fe7adfadf0752eb23","tid":2358542,"uid":9,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"香港人唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5571c20ac3e07d3d2c95d541fc7550a99c78bef2","tid":2358542,"uid":5020,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f5abe3f81e348dc9812d398fe7adfadf0752eb23","tid":2358542,"uid":9,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:15:43.000Z","msg":"香港人唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T08:19:25.000Z","msg":"所有旅客包括英國人都要檢驗<br />\n只係由香港去嘅人唔使到埗後隔離10日"},{"pid":"f11679d6e2b38330d8e4b4a6fbb23f5108337bdc","tid":2358542,"uid